{"tid":1416351,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【以正視聽】【集思廣益】【重要】8月5日爭議，反思","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:51:28.000Z","uid":204194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32b12d13bf0ea7b9dd210dc55834f816d5a6136c","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"首先，不割席、不分化。<br />\n其次，重申正視五大訴求，乃至六七八更多訴求。<br />\n<br />\n問題一：今日放火一事<br />\n１。沙田警署<br />\n有效防禦，較能說服及解釋動機，可以提升一般市民對抗爭力度嘅接受程度，拎經驗值，可接受<br />\n２。黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍<br />\n有效攻擊警家屬，但同時消防、救護等無辜人士亦受影響，輿論壓力較大，一次即可，可避免<br />\n３。其他零聲<br />\n如為防線<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內</span></span>並<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非</span></span>撤退，可能會TK，玩自己兼唔好聽，應避免<br />\n如為防線<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內外</span></span>並<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正</span></span>撤退，可接受<br />\n如為防線<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外</span></span>，即攻擊，武力程度個人不議論<br />\n總結，不割席、不分化，但唔代表唔學習、唔反思。<br />\n（歡迎補充，未清楚有冇其他放火）<br />\n<br />\n問題二：圍警署行動<br />\n１。破壞<strong></strong><br />\n玻璃，CAM冇傷大雅。車，小心爆炸。輿論大家諗。成效，對警察一係 fight or flight，同時表態示威者決心。<br />\n２。塗鴉<br />\n唔好只係屌狗，粗口，低俗野，可以有，但更需要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重申五大訴求</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">口號</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宣傳作用</span><br />\n總結，勿過份宣洩，忘記初衷，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冷靜行事</span></strong>！！！<br />\n<br />\n問題三：不合作運動<br />\n１。塞地鐵<br />\n好有用，但後果好大，冇實際數據講有幾多「中立」，淺黃市民有變，亦唔想誇大，但太多次都唔係人人都接受到。ＴＶＢ又可以洗人腦，林鄭有位入，甚至陰謀論講，可以做戲播俾人睇。<br />\n２。塞紅隧<br />\n有用，但唔好塞哂，留一條，後果同上。<br />\n總結，係大部分市民有心理準備長時間、多次罷工，暫時唔建議。更建議宣傳，叫市民自主罷工，但好難。<br />\n<br />\n問題四：對一般市民<br />\n１。影相<br />\n非影大頭，非鬼鬼鼠鼠，非多次影相，請友善、冷靜向市民解釋，請佢del相。<br />\n係鬼就自己諗諗點做好<br />\n２。危險駕駛<br />\n即屌，但唔好做得太難睇，要冷靜處理<br />\n３。郁手<br />\n<strong>警告</strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">壓制</span></strong>，唔好一味想打死人，有索帶用索帶<br />\n總結，禮貌、友善、做好榜樣<br />\n<br />\n問題五：一個都不能少<br />\n１。游擊時<br />\n前線唔好只係沖，要留意身邊同伴，一旦你落單，我好心痛。另外，一旦你太前，小心警用催淚彈射你後面，甚至你自己，一係直接受傷，一係斷你視野，唔知警沖＋隊友唔知可以點救你。<br />\n中後排散時要睇住前面，但唔好塞死，唔好唔理前線走咗<br />\n２。堅守時<br />\n今次唔錯，黃大仙幾成功<br />\n總結，非軍師，只可以講要冷靜，諗清楚自己做緊乜，打狗可以，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前提係你知道自己點走到</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n題外話：文宣，口號，唔好少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大總結：BE WATER，水可以柔軟的流動，也可以堅硬的凝結。冷靜思考，再冷靜思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n請集思廣益。"},{"pid":"32b4d0f35d6db54040e8739898d491655c73e7b7","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"大家請俾意見，亦推俾多啲人睇。"},{"pid":"d57d88732aefcb0d04c708e9a3aa78e165ac40e1","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1b5317616b9199b5cd668be8f2e5f157aba15f6","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"edfbecc78a19d2af1ca0ffc8593faffddff54296","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d3abe6f046d007206291030259623550adcf5b2a","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4a78ac9abdcbffeddd838e5c264bd0aa420c2d7","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15e1171d6f54455e092377e7bd031dbaa88aa3cf","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4114f7eeb16e88e7382710733b64ec7ba2acdbd","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"33fd7cdf20fbffbdbad6a4a4816dd630abbb29d3","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d8114964e5ce230eab6dc2a6548e0d2f55ae72a","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff8bc3e71dc351356f490381552cb54f80681c0d","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"58004f91df7138ba55b23d022f875d4200203775","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d62ebeb495fed7243840e6820ee933b30391bed","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"46f3923dab40577c48099fded6223caf152545d7","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e193fbf6e930ba8ff08722094169fa41d0f2459","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f4e26ef90bfb3d07838db690812e6142afe0e35","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14ff46370e04c71fa3303474ad6cf3f9305e0b8b","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eac7f512e64dcb869f01a3548009648e89be6f87","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"280c01fb70f2afd84e28502cf6cfa9f582b7c14f","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"667514d20c2880e2c44fa0539ce53b406362e1ea","tid":1416351,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"push"}]}